{% raw %} 
byte = 8
gigabit = 10 ** 9
bandwidth = gigabit / byte
duration = 3
file_size = 10 ** 7

epoch = Epoch(
    file_size=file_size,
    duration=3,
    bandwith=bandwidth,
)

r = httpx.post(url, json=epoch.dict())
print(r.status_code, r.json())
